# RR Infra Refine Canon Base

```yaml
components:
  - atd
  - "hace_io (moved to rr/infra/io/hace)"
  - hacetime
  - haceto
  - hasi
responsibilities:
  - sanctioned refine engines
  - optimization and syscall hardening boundaries
  - refine-safe extension contracts
rules:
  - Refine engines may optimize behavior but must not weaken authority, ABI, or execution determinism.
```
